         MACRO                                                          00160000
.*                                                                      00170000
.* This macro generates OPSYNs for a list of opcodes                    00180000
.*                                                                      00190000
         OPSYNS ,                      * Arguments in &SYSLIST          00200000
.*                                                                      00210000
.* &SYSLIST - each entry specifies an opcode or directive which will    00220000
.*            be replaced by its underscore-prefixed equivalent         00230000
.*                                                                      00240000
.********************************************************************** 00241001
.*                                                                      00242001
.*       IMPORTANT NOTICE                                               00243001
.*       ========= ======                                               00244001
